  "commentary": "**DEALER HEDGING COMMENTARY:**\n\nWith SPX at 6766.79 sitting 13.21 points below the GEX flip at 6780, dealers are currently in a PIN regime where they're long gamma and will sell any rallies while buying dips. The massive positive gamma wall at 6780 (+15.8B) creates strong resistance as dealers will aggressively sell delta hedges on any move higher, while the negative gamma pocket at 6750 (-8.0B) provides support where dealers flip to buying. The 379% GEX surge in 5 minutes indicates heavy options flow just hit, likely creating this pronounced gamma profile that should pin price action between 6750-6780.\n\n**Bottom line:** expect the market to get stuck between 6750 and 6780 with dealers capping rallies.",
